---
import SectionHeading from "../../components/SectionHeading.astro";
---
<section id="storyboard-exports" class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <SectionHeading
        eyebrow="Animatic & exports"
        title="Preview timing, collect feedback, ship every format"
        description="Assign durations, transitions, and audio notes to each panel. Spin up review contact sheets, render MP4/GIF animatics, and export press-ready PDFs or vertical scrolls."
        align="center"
        containerClass="max-w-3xl"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr] lg:items-center">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 text-left text-sm text-slate-700">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Animatic timeline</h3>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Set per-panel timing, choose transitions (cut, dissolve, pan), and mark camera moves. Preview in-app or render
            straight to GIF/MP4 for sharing.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-wave-square text-indigo-500"></i>
              <span>Adjust easing curves for pans and zooms</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-music text-indigo-500"></i>
              <span>Attach audio cues or VO references per beat</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-share-nodes text-indigo-500"></i>
              <span>Render low-res previews while high-res export processes</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 text-left text-sm text-slate-700">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Review center</h3>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Generate thumbnails, contact sheets, and version snapshots. Stakeholders can comment, resolve notes, and view
            change history without editing privileges.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-comments text-indigo-500"></i>
              <span>Threaded feedback tied to panels and balloons</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-bookmark text-indigo-500"></i>
              <span>Tag milestones like "roughs", "inks", "tones"</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-shuffle text-indigo-500"></i>
              <span>Compare versions side-by-side before approvals</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -left-6 top-6 h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-indigo-200/50 blur-xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute -right-8 bottom-6 h-24 w-24 rounded-full bg-purple-200/50 blur-2xl"></div>
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2.25rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-xl">
          <div class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-6 py-4 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-slate-500">
            Export presets
          </div>
          <div class="divide-y divide-slate-200 text-sm text-slate-700">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Print PDF</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Bleed, trim, and live safe areas included</p>
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-indigo-500">Pro</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900">PNG page stack</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Individual panels auto-named</p>
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400">Free</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Webtoon scroll</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Merge selected pages into tall strip</p>
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-indigo-500">Pro</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Animatic MP4</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Watermark optional Â· 1080p</p>
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-indigo-500">Pro</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900">GIF preview</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Share lightweight loops with teams</p>
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400">Free</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 px-6 py-4 text-xs text-slate-500">
            Send exports directly to Presentation Designer or Archive vault.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
